subject: Re: [junit] Query on estimation
msgSnippet: ... Is the code already written, or are you practicing TDD to write new features? How much /experience/ do the other 3 people have with JUnit already? -- J. B.
messageBody:

>
> Dear all,
>
> I would like to use JUnits for a development project. Can somebody guide

features?
